{"tid":2293130,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"逃出支那最大半導體騙局 蔣尚義：我在支那武漢弘芯的經歷根本是場噩夢","createTime":"2020-11-20T04:42:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-20T08:18:54.000Z","uid":32511,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"ff068217e98cf9ae84957a4379c0095b5a2d2708","tid":2293130,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T04:42:51.000Z","msg":"中國為建立芯片供應的自主，近年來以舉國之力發展半導體產業，卻催生被稱為「中國最大<br />\n半導體騙局」的武漢弘芯，該公司今年因財務問題嚴重，確定被中國地方政府接管，再度顯<br />\n示中國在追求自產晶片這條路上的挫敗。而「武漢弘芯」去年才高薪挖角大批台積電員工，<br />\n還延攬前台積電共同營運長蔣尚義擔任執行長，如今因為瀕臨破產、公司營運陷入停擺，連<br />\n被視為是弘芯招牌的前執行長蔣尚義都對此坦言「根本是場噩夢」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://reurl.cc/0Obgxo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Freurl.cc%2F0Obgxo&d=gxBKi3yaaNwv0eARaXv6BXlPKE5%2BvOhv5kPCmhOEeDs%3D&h=9e1839db\" target=\"_blank\">https://reurl.cc/0Obgxo</a>"},{"pid":"c78f1fc9dec6778f80b732e9e901b95ba635a486","tid":2293130,"uid":55043,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T04:44:40.000Z","msg":"台灣on9佬咁都中伏唔抵爭"},{"pid":"20a51cebb3ea8b5aea6037ebac82216abbc51112","tid":2293130,"uid":182624,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T04:45:56.000Z","msg":"仲番唔番到台積電呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfbabd80098278127df946b7c2bc3d8ecbb6a05a","tid":2293130,"uid":8308,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T04:46:31.000Z","msg":"自己抵死怪邊個<br />\n高薪請你返去唔洗付出代價?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e49a041743007d21143baafdf06b23ed829f8833","tid":2293130,"uid":36911,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T04:46:55.000Z","msg":"佢仲走唔走得出支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70c467923d47918236c8ff633ad1151701cdf9f0","tid":2293130,"uid":32511,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T04:47:30.000Z","msg":"想返支那大灣區工作嘅自己留意<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji